nal Medical Education Ordinance, 2074 brought by addressing Prof Dr KC\u2019s demands.\n\n\u201cIf these issues were followed well, the medical education sector could see good progress,\u201d he underscored, appealing to the federal government to take the right track regarding Dr KC\u2019s agitation.","title":"NC appeals to government for meaningful talks with Dr KC - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/23/129890/","video":[]}
